metadata.name: Ordinal Goblin #1
metadata.description: Ordinal Goblin is a collection of 100 Goblins inscribed in the #3800-25000 range in Bitcoin. In order to redeem your inscription in Ordinaland, you must sacrifice 50 Goblins in the Abyss of Ethereum. Link to the inscription list: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1_j-OduJuHZ9Ejya7BmKn4_fZPghzMCXcLnNW4iihmXc/edit?usp=sharing
